Toolroom Selector Series: 23 Harry Romero (2014) 

                        Tech House | Toolroom Longplayer

               320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 01:47:52 | 247 Mb


For the next edition in our long-standing Selector Series we've chosen New York's finest DJ & producer, Harry Romero to carefully select his all-time favourite Toolroom tracks. Romero has been making serious waves in the Dance scene for a long time and now has an impressive musical CV which features collabs with Joeski, Doorly, Erick Morillo, MYNC, Jose Nunez as well as producing remixes for Josh Wink, Coyu, Ramiro Lopez, Eddie Thoneick and releasing his music on some of the most influential labels in the industry including Toolroom, Subliminal, Circus, Strictly Rhythm & Ovum.

With a star-studded track list featuring the works of Kevin Saunderson, Jay Lumen, Tong & Rogers, Pirupa, Wehbba, Mihalis Safras, Matthias Tanzmann, Ramon Tapia, Doomwork & more, and featuring some of Harry's best works including his sensational 2014 rework of the infamous 'Tania' as well as his brilliant collab with Junior Sanchez 'San Real'. Showcasing a massive 15 tracks plus an intricate full-length DJ mix, 'Toolroom Selector Series 23: Harry Romero' is another exemplary edition in the series; sure to be appreciated and enjoyed by House-heads across the globe.
